{
  "stem": "198.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my brother, who lives now in New York, he said, if my sister survived, [SIGHS] that is a miracle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody said that probably they were kapos, they were killers, because we had a lot of bad people in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said-- my brother said, I know where I'm coming from.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If my sister survived, this was plain luck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He jumped on a train and he hitchhiked to Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Took about-- this was 1945 in December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I stayed [SIGHS] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I stayed in Lodz for about a few days hoping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know that he survived, that he's coming back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, I couldn't stay so long in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Somehow I went back to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my sister stayed in Lodz with my friend, Bella, and Bella's sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We all paired up, whoever survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one date, December, New Year's, I stayed-- I met some people in Dachau after the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Which we survived the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We just, we're going with no aim.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I met some friends in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she had a brother which survived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he had already a home, take me away from a German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we had a roof over our head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know what-- where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, I-- [DRINKS] New Year's Eve I was-- I was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "New Year's Eve, I was hoping that I'm going to meet somebody from my family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So from Bad Kudowa, from Czechoslovakia, I went to Regensburg, which is a border town from Germany, you know, Germany to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was hoping that maybe, maybe this is the night I'm going to reunite with my family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Went to Regensburg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everywhere they formed DP camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I went to the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
